    "We considered the following functionalization variants: 𝑁 𝑂𝐻 /𝑁 • 100% = 0, 10, 30, 50, 70, 90, 100%.",
    "The simulation procedure was as follows: first, the system was heated and thermalized at 300 K for 0.35 ns in the NVT ensemble.",
